title: The Developer submitting the scheme shall also furnish Scrutiny Fee as prescribed and as decided by the C
clause_text: The Developer submitting the scheme shall also furnish Scrutiny Fee as prescribed and as decided by the C.E.O., S.R.A. Pune from time to time. Approval to the S.R.S. shall be given by the C.E.O., S.R.A. in accordance with the said Regulations.
